title: Is TikTok taking over Instagram?
description:
This week on Fool Coverage, Manny and Laura talk about the death of Instagram... your favorite app turned copycat. They cover the horrible glitches on reels, how it copies other apps like TikTok, issues with the algorithm, and much more! Tune in til the end for some Disney Trivia!
Follow Laura on IG: @larlarlee
Follow Manny on IG: @mannymua733
